Early Ethereum depositors will enjoy staking at 20% monthly in addition to the 40% Airdrop bonus for the first 1 year. This exchange platform will be safe and super-fast in matching millions of trade orders in quickest time possible!  Trading/Arbitrage bot  Our beta-tested trading/arbitrage bot guarantees a monthly return of 15-20%. Profits generated will reflect real market scenarios. LOANING & STAKING  Trabet Coin is originally for trading and betting but will encourage LOANING; initially, for the first 1,000 interested investors to earn higher daily returns for agreed locked-in-period.
